Team Data

Source: R/data_doc.R
team_data.Rd

A dataset containing information about various cheerleading teams.

Usage

team_data

Format

A data frame with X rows and Y columns:

name

A character vector of team names.

url

A character vector of team namuwiki urls.

color

A character vector of team themesong urls on YouTube.

Details

This dataset includes columns such as team names, locations, and performance metrics.

Examples

data(team_data)
head(team_data)
